    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Hand tools consisting of a steel or other metal head pointed at one or both ends and mounted on a handle or wood or another material; used for loosening and breaking up compacted soil or rocks.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
